    "captions": [
      {
        "text": "The deadliest Olympic marathon wasn\u2019t a war. It was a joke.",
        "position": {
          "start": 0.0,
          "end": 4.4
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Ninety-degree heat, zero water stations, and a route full of dust.",
        "position": {
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "One runner chugged rat poison just to stay awake.",
        "position": {
          "start": 8.72,
          "end": 13.96
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Another hitched a ride in a passing automobile.",
        "position": {
          "start": 9.6,
          "end": 12.8
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "A third sprinted away from a pack of wild dogs.",
        "position": {
          "start": 14.7,
          "end": 21.06
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "The eventual winner actually stopped to take a quick afternoon nap.",
        "position": {
          "start": 22.0,
          "end": 26.4
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "He crossed the finish line completely delirious, carried by handlers.",
        "position": {
          "start": 21.76,
          "end": 24.92
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Organizers banned performance enhancers after this absolute circus.",
        "position": {
          "start": 25.68,
          "end": 28.9
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "History erased it because it made the Olympics look foolish.",
        "position": {
          "start": 29.9,
          "end": 32.5
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Follow for more forgotten moments they skipped in class.",
        "position": {
